POWERTIP IMAGE CORPORATION, 10 years experience in optical field, we dedicate in plastic lens field and provide you the best experiences of cooperation.
        　 
        From optical design, mold design to injection, assembly and coating, we are the professional lens provider that can serve you total solution in optical field.
        　
        With various of product line, we can offer you in full series application lenses, camera phone module, NB cam module, PC camera, web camera….
		　
		Quality, Service and Fast response are 3 elements of our company discipline.


