Company Information
   

Contact Us




We supply LCM to big names Powertip, established in 1991 has been focusing on development and manufacturing of Liquid Crystal Modules (LCMs) for over 15 years. With superior Surface Mounted Devices (SMTs), Chip On Board (COB) technology, and Tape-Automatic Bonding (TAB) technology, we provide world class LCMs to clients such as Motorola, Simens, Matsushita and the like. Displays f... More...


We supply LCM to big names Powertip, established in 1991 has been focusing on development and manufacturing of Liquid Crystal Modules (LCMs) for over 15 years. With superior Surface Mounted Devices (SMTs), Chip On Board (COB) technology, and Tape-Automatic Bonding (TAB) technology, we provide world class LCMs to clients such as Motorola, Simens, Matsushita and the like. Displays for a full range of personal communication devices To increase competitiveness in the cell phone, PDA and E-book markets, we provide a full depth of SMT, COB, TAB and COG for Mono, CSTN and TFT Displays. Branch offices on three continents Headquartered in Taichung, Taiwan we have also established manufacturing sites in Dongguan, Zhenjiang China, and branch offices in Hong Kong, Shenzhen, Shanghai, Beijing, LA and Germany. We will continue to develop sales channels around the globe to better serve customers like you. When sourcing displays from us, you will enjoy easy and effective communication and ordering flexibility. See the quality of our products for yourself --- call us to request a sample today.

Business type:ManufacturerStaff:3,000 to 3,499Year Established:1991








