Powertip Technology Corporation

- Taiwan
				
				


















































Powetip Technoloty Corporation was established in 1991, since then it has focused on development and manufacturing of its own Liquid Crystal Module(LCM) to supply the global demand of LCM. With its superior Surface Mound Device(SMT), Chip On Board(COB), and Tape-Automatic Bording(TAB)technology, Powertip has been providing world class LCM to its customers. After a decade, Powertip has become a premiem LCM brand name and has gained the acceptance of Motorb, Siemens, Matsushita.
Powetip Technoloty Corporation was established in 1991, since then it has focused on development and manufacturing of its own Liquid Crystal Module(LCM) to supply the global demand of LCM. With its superior Surface Mound Device(SMT), Chip On Board(COB), and Tape-Automatic Bording(TAB)technology, Powertip has been providing world class LCM to its customers. After a decade, Powertip has become a premiem LCM brand name and has gained the acceptance of Motorb, Siemens, Matsushita.Less





















